items.name: High Point Networks
items.description:
High Point Networks is a value-added reseller (VAR) of information technology providing solutions to both the SMB and enterprise level markets in the upper Great Plains. We offer organizations best-in-class voice and data networking solutions, supported by the best professional services team in the region. Our solutions solve real challenges and provide measurable return on investment.

Established in 2003, High Point Networks has quickly become one of the region's premier providers of voice and data network solutions. High Point Networks has been based in West Fargo, North Dakota since its inception. The company has 120+ employees in offices throughout the midwest. There are currently offices in Bismarck, Sioux Falls, Brookings, Billings, Detroit Lakes, Minneapolis and Denver. High Point Networks moved to its new corporate office building in West Fargo in November 2013. The company acquired the VAR division of EarthBend, LLC based in Sioux Falls in August 2017.

items.name: Benes Enterprises, Inc. dba One of a Kind Solutions
items.description:
At One of a Kind Solutions, our mission is to help businesses realize the potential benefits of technology and how they can use technology to improve their daily business operations. Technology should be something that is turned to and used as a valuable resource, not a last-ditch effort. When used correctly, technology has the potential to change the way that your business operates, driving your bottom line and increasing profitability. We want to help you get there.

There are several steps we take to achieve our mission. First, we simplify technology. There are so many options and choices, let us present you with what you need and assist you with beginning to use these new technologies. Simple is beautiful. Second, we support technology. We are here as a constant resource to assist you with your needs. Constant and effective communication is key. Third, we’re here to help you plan for the future. Don’t be blindsided by new technology, let us help you embrace and adopt the latest technology so you can have a leg up on your competitors.

We have a variety of services to meet the needs of your business. We offer disaster recovery to ensure your mission-critical files are protected, email marketing to increase customer loyalty, website design to create a powerful image on the web, and more. We’d love to meet with you to learn about your goals and desires in order to develop a plan that is right for your business.

All of our services come standard with our passion for technology, desire to see your business succeed, rapid and effective communication, and innovation to meet all the unique challenges that you may bring to the table.

Interested? We’d love to hear from you!
